Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.40,0:00:11.48,Default,,0,0,0,,你不懂啊 橘 一点都不懂
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.13,0:00:14.20,Default,,0,0,0,,要是你跟我约会 肯定得憋屈死了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.56,0:00:16.74,Default,,0,0,0,,你愿意跟我约会吗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.88,0:00:18.95,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯对 约会…咦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.72,0:00:22.35,Default,,0,0,0,,你刚刚提到了约会吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.59,0:00:24.28,Default,,0,0,0,,刚…刚刚我的意思是…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.87,0:00:24.73,Default,,0,0,0,,你刚刚说了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.21,0:00:28.69,Default,,0,0,0,,我是说了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.23,0:00:35.51,Default,,0,0,0,,一个仆人站在罗生门下等待雨停
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.28,0:00:39.86,Default,,0,0,0,,宽敞的门下 只有这个男子在
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.55,0:00:44.74,Default,,0,0,0,,只是四处朱漆剥落的大圆柱上
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.16,0:00:47.14,Default,,0,0,0,,停着一只蟋蟀
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.94,0:00:50.48,Default,,0,0,0,,罗生门既然建在朱雀大路上
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.94,0:00:52.36,Default,,0,0,0,,除了这个男子
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.81,0:00:55.66,Default,,0,0,0,,总该还有三三两两戴着蓑笠的女子
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.99,0:00:58.37,Default,,0,0,0,,和戴着乌帽的男子避雨
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.79,0:01:01.33,Default,,0,0,0,,但此时 却只有这个男子
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.03,0:01:02.95,Screen,,0,0,0,,# 店长 晶
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.96,0:02:31.79,Default,,0,0,0,,【OP】
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.80,0:02:38.55,Episode Title,,0,0,0,,# 第4集 细雨纷纷
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.06,0:02:38.38,Default,,0,0,0,,您好 您说的没错
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.19,0:02:38.37,Default,,0,0,0,,# 好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.00,0:02:40.06,Default,,0,0,0,,是 是
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.72,0:02:44.57,Default,,0,0,0,,非常抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.88,0:02:48.40,Default,,0,0,0,,是 是 您说的不错
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.86,0:02:50.85,Default,,0,0,0,,是 今后会多加留心
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.55,0:02:54.70,Default,,0,0,0,,是 那我挂了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.85,0:03:00.06,Default,,0,0,0,,加濑 你倒是把头发理理啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.06,0:03:02.97,Default,,0,0,0,,对不起 下次来之前会剃的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.56,0:03:05.34,Default,,0,0,0,,上次你也这么说的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.53,0:03:08.83,Default,,0,0,0,,换了张新排班表 你看下
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.33,0:03:09.86,Default,,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.89,0:03:20.72,Default,,0,0,0,,你好
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.48,0:03:23.13,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯 你好
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.21,0:03:36.30,Default,,0,0,0,,店长 您周六放假吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.88,0:03:40.83,Default,,0,0,0,,我看新排班表的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.18,0:03:45.14,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯 我放假
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.56,0:03:46.74,Default,,0,0,0,,我也放假
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.64,0:03:50.89,Default,,0,0,0,,关于之前说的那事…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.60,0:03:54.64,Default,,0,0,0,,什么事
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.14,0:03:58.12,Default,,0,0,0,,就是您愿意和我约会…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.79,0:04:01.37,Default,,0,0,0,,那件事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.28,0:04:02.36,Default,,0,0,0,,周六可以吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.15,0:04:03.77,Default,,0,0,0,,周六？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.08,0:04:04.49,Default,,0,0,0,,约会
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.12,0:04:06.57,Default,,0,0,0,,这个…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.69,0:04:07.56,Default,,0,0,0,,请和我约会
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.36,0:04:09.04,Default,,0,0,0,,啊…是
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.59,0:04:10.46,Default,,0,0,0,,约好了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.28,0:04:11.67,Default,,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.90,0:04:15.01,Default,,0,0,0,,请多关照
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.85,0:04:23.19,Default,,0,0,0,,打工吗 我就在打工
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.33,0:04:29.99,Default,,0,0,0,,你说当家教啊 时薪多少
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.28,0:04:35.80,Default,,0,0,0,,价格挺高的啊 教高中生吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.65,0:04:39.59,Default,,0,0,0,,英语啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.63,0:04:45.19,Default,,0,0,0,,做得来的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.66,0:04:51.58,Default,,0,0,0,,那还真不错
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.10,0:04:58.68,Default,,0,0,0,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.39,0:05:01.42,Default,,0,0,0,,那个高中妹正不
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.01,0:05:04.54,Default,,0,0,0,,什么 是个臭小子？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.54,0:05:05.32,Default,,0,0,0,,那做个毛线
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.52,0:05:08.44,Default,,0,0,0,,要教高中生 给我找个妹子来
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.99,0:05:10.19,Default,,0,0,0,,现在都闲着呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.47,0:05:12.89,Default,,0,0,0,,感觉真难过
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.89,0:05:14.32,Default,,0,0,0,,真的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.36,0:05:16.96,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯 我把上个月的钱花光了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.96,0:05:18.23,Default,,0,0,0,,打柏青哥吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.50,0:05:18.97,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.27,0:05:22.21,Default,,0,0,0,,你这玩太大了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.83,0:05:25.76,Default,,0,0,0,,加濑 你也来听啊 大塚他
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.20,0:05:28.05,Default,,0,0,0,,橘 想吃点什么
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.85,0:05:31.24,Default,,0,0,0,,三明治吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.60,0:05:33.25,Default,,0,0,0,,知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.71,0:05:39.56,Default,,0,0,0,,橘晶 高中二年级
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.34,0:05:43.43,Default,,0,0,0,,算这个年纪冷淡的了 喜怒很少形于色
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.00,0:06:11.08,Default,,0,0,0,,想太多了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.80,0:06:20.11,Default,,0,0,0,,橘 你的吃的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.20,0:06:22.13,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.98,0:06:27.09,Default,,0,0,0,,她刚刚看什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.61,0:06:30.70,Default,,0,0,0,,加濑 这是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.30,0:06:35.42,Default,,0,0,0,,这个啊 我请你的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.99,0:06:39.46,Default,,0,0,0,,谢了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.61,0:06:45.95,Default,,0,0,0,,真够冷的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.79,0:07:10.38,Default,,0,0,0,,好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.74,0:07:11.61,Default,,0,0,0,,你好
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.12,0:07:14.15,Default,,0,0,0,,这就休息好了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.51,0:07:14.95,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.18,0:07:19.08,Default,,0,0,0,,你刚刚在念书吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.45,0:07:21.04,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯 要考试了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.59,0:07:23.99,Default,,0,0,0,,我好久没见到高中课本了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.20,0:07:27.49,Default,,0,0,0,,能让我看看吗 不行吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.70,0:07:29.70,Default,,0,0,0,,那你看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.47,0:07:31.08,Default,,0,0,0,,谢了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.48,0:07:35.27,Default,,0,0,0,,看完丢在这里就好
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.02,0:07:36.72,Default,,0,0,0,,OK
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.48,0:07:40.50,Default,,0,0,0,,我吃好了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.87,0:07:50.70,Default,,0,0,0,,欢迎光临 几位客人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.95,0:07:51.48,Default,,0,0,0,,两位
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.06,0:07:53.80,Default,,0,0,0,,要吸烟席还是无烟席
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.01,0:07:54.46,Default,,0,0,0,,无烟席
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.04,0:07:58.07,Default,,0,0,0,,知道了 请随便坐吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.76,0:08:14.20,Default,,0,0,0,,不行啊 上课还涂鸦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.88,0:08:20.33,Default,,0,0,0,,请你不要跟别人说
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.24,0:08:23.85,Default,,0,0,0,,这倒无妨
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.62,0:08:29.57,Default,,0,0,0,,不过相对的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.08,0:08:32.18,Default,,0,0,0,,陪我约个会吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.93,0:08:34.57,Default,,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.55,0:08:43.31,Default,,0,0,0,,加濑
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.60,0:08:47.79,Default,,0,0,0,,你今天上学的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.05,0:08:48.47,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.06,0:08:50.91,Default,,0,0,0,,还回家换了衣服吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.26,0:08:51.78,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.92,0:08:54.30,Default,,0,0,0,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.25,0:08:56.15,Default,,0,0,0,,那我们走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.56,0:09:20.99,Default,,0,0,0,,给
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.53,0:09:22.00,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.45,0:09:25.24,Default,,0,0,0,,很可怕的片子喔 能看吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.98,0:09:29.37,Default,,0,0,0,,害怕就握紧我的手吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.26,0:09:32.86,Default,,0,0,0,,工作日可真空啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.36,0:09:33.97,Default,,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.32,0:09:43.08,Default,,0,0,0,,你不是去美甲沙龙了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.34,0:09:44.32,Default,,0,0,0,,内森 你快跑
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.58,0:09:47.19,Default,,0,0,0,,她不是我们认识的安洁莉卡了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.19,0:09:49.10,Default,,0,0,0,,不会吧 安洁莉卡
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.46,0:09:51.89,Default,,0,0,0,,是我啊 还记得吗 记得就接着…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.62,0:09:55.34,Default,,0,0,0,,天啊 安洁莉卡
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.92,0:09:59.64,Default,,0,0,0,,你要回去了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.59,0:10:01.72,Default,,0,0,0,,肚子不饿吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.94,0:10:05.88,Default,,0,0,0,,妈妈给我做晚饭了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.26,0:10:07.85,Default,,0,0,0,,这些你拿着
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.61,0:10:10.24,Default,,0,0,0,,电影票 宣传册和可乐的钱
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.66,0:10:18.48,Default,,0,0,0,,咖啡馆坐坐吧 这才叫约会
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.02,0:10:20.09,Default,,0,0,0,,欢迎光临
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.08,0:10:25.11,Default,,0,0,0,,请慢用
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.97,0:10:37.92,Default,,0,0,0,,橘是田径社的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.56,0:10:40.76,Default,,0,0,0,,以前是
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.80,0:10:43.18,Default,,0,0,0,,听说受伤就退社了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.01,0:10:46.85,Default,,0,0,0,,吉泽说你以前跑得可快了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.14,0:10:49.49,Default,,0,0,0,,反正都过去了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.92,0:10:54.33,Default,,0,0,0,,热衷的东西一夜间消失无踪 是什么感觉
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.76,0:10:56.82,Default,,0,0,0,,抱歉让你不开心了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.38,0:10:58.70,Default,,0,0,0,,反正事情也都过去了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.34,0:11:06.24,Default,,0,0,0,,当时很沮丧 但现在已经无所谓了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.80,0:11:07.71,Default,,0,0,0,,打工很有趣
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.29,0:11:09.44,Default,,0,0,0,,而且有店长在？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.96,0:11:12.46,Default,,0,0,0,,今天你第一次正脸看我
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.47,0:11:16.43,Default,,0,0,0,,这约会我陪过了 你会帮我保密的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.29,0:11:18.78,Default,,0,0,0,,这就叫约会啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.22,0:11:25.04,Default,,0,0,0,,我看就是 喜欢的田径跑不成了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.04,0:11:26.62,Default,,0,0,0,,所以就恋爱了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.19,0:11:30.45,Default,,0,0,0,,但对象是45岁的大叔 不恶心吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.53,0:11:34.16,Default,,0,0,0,,我回了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.52,0:11:41.33,Default,,0,0,0,,等等 你不用掏钱的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.16,0:11:43.89,Default,,0,0,0,,等等啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.16,0:11:47.04,Default,,0,0,0,,请放开我
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.54,0:11:51.61,Default,,0,0,0,,电话啊 对方是…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.64,0:11:54.12,Default,,0,0,0,,店长
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.01,0:11:57.47,Default,,0,0,0,,想接吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.48,0:12:07.99,Default,,0,0,0,,喂 喂
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.96,0:12:10.04,Default,,0,0,0,,我是“花园”的近藤
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.16,0:12:12.08,Default,,0,0,0,,现在方便说话吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.19,0:12:13.70,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.27,0:12:16.53,Default,,0,0,0,,那个…关于和我…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.28,0:12:20.16,Default,,0,0,0,,约会的那件事
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.73,0:12:22.49,Default,,0,0,0,,你有什么想去的地方吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.84,0:12:27.48,Default,,0,0,0,,去你想去的地方就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.31,0:12:29.26,Default,,0,0,0,,这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.87,0:12:31.53,Default,,0,0,0,,那我得好好想一下啰
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.65,0:12:34.19,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯 麻烦你了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.60,0:12:55.08,Default,,0,0,0,,你就那么喜欢他？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.60,0:13:01.71,Default,,0,0,0,,你和店长是不会顺利的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.30,0:13:03.08,Default,,0,0,0,,绝对不会
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.95,0:13:05.83,Default,,0,0,0,,我不是在唱衰你哦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.65,0:13:09.66,Default,,0,0,0,,是叫你来点更健全恋爱的…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.91,0:13:22.08,Default,,0,0,0,,建议罢了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.37,0:13:25.13,Default,,0,0,0,,今天就这样吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.12,0:13:28.55,Default,,0,0,0,,我们下次再继续
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.72,0:13:37.32,Default,,0,0,0,,欢迎回来
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.26,0:13:40.62,Default,,0,0,0,,这电影看起来不错啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.23,0:13:42.97,Default,,0,0,0,,真的要丢掉吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.23,0:13:46.10,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯 帮我丢了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.86,0:13:56.96,Default,,0,0,0,,我是“花园”的近藤
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.44,0:14:11.49,Default,,0,0,0,,你和店长是不会顺利的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.01,0:14:24.58,Default,,0,0,0,,是在这儿碰面的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.47,0:14:27.24,Default,,0,0,0,,好想抽根烟
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.60,0:14:30.37,Default,,0,0,0,,我去抽根烟好了？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.27,0:14:33.88,Default,,0,0,0,,不过要是她刚好来了就糟了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.98,0:14:35.59,Default,,0,0,0,,店长
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.51,0:14:40.04,Default,,0,0,0,,让…让您久等了 不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.49,0:14:42.97,Default,,0,0,0,,那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.11,0:14:45.69,Default,,0,0,0,,你和平时不太一样耶
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.85,0:14:49.72,Default,,0,0,0,,因为我…换了个发型
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.01,0:14:54.30,Default,,0,0,0,,那我们走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.40,0:14:55.91,Default,,0,0,0,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.37,0:15:02.04,Default,,0,0,0,,你不是去美甲沙龙了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.25,0:15:03.26,Default,,0,0,0,,内森 你快跑
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.52,0:15:06.07,Default,,0,0,0,,她不是我们认识的安洁莉卡了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.07,0:15:07.99,Default,,0,0,0,,不会吧 安洁莉卡
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.41,0:15:10.68,Default,,0,0,0,,是我啊 还记得吗 记得就接着…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.71,0:15:13.88,Default,,0,0,0,,安洁莉卡
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.88,0:15:14.70,Default,,0,0,0,,内森
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.08,0:15:17.90,Default,,0,0,0,,这电影真好看啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.36,0:15:21.19,Default,,0,0,0,,我跟勇斗一起 就不能看这种电影
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.02,0:15:23.04,Default,,0,0,0,,橘 你觉得好看吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.24,0:15:24.70,Default,,0,0,0,,那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.40,0:15:28.39,Default,,0,0,0,,是部看几遍都很好看的电影
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.32,0:15:31.44,Default,,0,0,0,,这样啊 真是太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.88,0:15:34.07,Default,,0,0,0,,那我们回家吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.60,0:15:35.32,Default,,0,0,0,,电影也看完了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.45,0:15:39.48,Default,,0,0,0,,我嘴巴有点渴
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.91,0:15:39.96,Default,,0,0,0,,欢迎光临
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.04,0:15:42.62,Default,,0,0,0,,请问两位要点餐吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.36,0:15:46.88,Default,,0,0,0,,那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.78,0:15:49.15,Default,,0,0,0,,柳橙冰茶一杯
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.64,0:15:50.15,Default,,0,0,0,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.69,0:15:54.64,Default,,0,0,0,,我要…那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.55,0:15:58.80,Default,,0,0,0,,吉力马札罗山咖啡 热的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.16,0:16:00.14,Default,,0,0,0,,我明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.39,0:16:03.34,Default,,0,0,0,,最近眼睛老花严重了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.97,0:16:11.18,Default,,0,0,0,,抱歉 咱太大叔了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.83,0:16:15.24,Default,,0,0,0,,你经常来这里吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.31,0:16:18.83,Default,,0,0,0,,没有 呃…偶尔会吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.30,0:16:20.75,Default,,0,0,0,,这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.18,0:16:24.90,Default,,0,0,0,,店长 您要几颗？（您几岁了？）
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.36,0:16:27.00,Default,,0,0,0,,咦 45岁（45颗）
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.18,0:16:27.00,Reference,,0,0,0,,# 日语这句话表意模糊，的确会弄错啦（
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.78,0:16:34.97,Reference,,0,0,0,,# 一颗 两颗 三颗 四颗 五颗 六颗 七颗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.29,0:16:31.14,Default,,0,0,0,,你是指砂糖啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.56,0:16:32.33,Default,,0,0,0,,我不要加糖
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.48,0:16:36.25,Default,,0,0,0,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.59,0:16:38.19,Default,,0,0,0,,没关系 没关系
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.74,0:16:42.19,Default,,0,0,0,,好甜
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.57,0:16:46.16,Default,,0,0,0,,这个味道
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.74,0:16:51.75,Default,,0,0,0,,第一次约会 我想耍帅就点了黑咖啡
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.64,0:16:54.07,Default,,0,0,0,,但实在太苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.80,0:16:56.59,Default,,0,0,0,,所以趁她去厕所时
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.91,0:16:58.62,Default,,0,0,0,,我赶紧加了好多糖块
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.28,0:17:06.20,Default,,0,0,0,,甜蜜又苦涩 这才是青春的味道
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.40,0:17:14.45,Default,,0,0,0,,欢迎光临
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.48,0:17:17.87,Default,,0,0,0,,话说回来 刚才的电影…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.44,0:17:19.52,Default,,0,0,0,,真不好形容
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.53,0:17:21.40,Default,,0,0,0,,就是说啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.43,0:17:23.63,Default,,0,0,0,,咦 真的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.63,0:17:24.85,Default,,0,0,0,,真的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.73,0:17:26.67,Default,,0,0,0,,好厉害哦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.24,0:17:28.16,Default,,0,0,0,,接下来要去哪呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.40,0:17:29.84,Default,,0,0,0,,去阿舜想去的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.84,0:17:30.57,Default,,0,0,0,,交给我决定？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.67,0:17:31.44,Default,,0,0,0,,这店怎么回事？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.36,0:17:33.61,Default,,0,0,0,,全都是年轻人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.29,0:17:39.89,Default,,0,0,0,,店长？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.18,0:17:44.10,Default,,0,0,0,,差不多该走了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.88,0:17:46.72,Default,,0,0,0,,不用收据 谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.43,0:17:48.80,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢惠顾
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.12,0:17:52.48,Default,,0,0,0,,那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.75,0:17:53.19,Default,,0,0,0,,请说
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.73,0:17:54.37,Default,,0,0,0,,可以给我吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.56,0:18:14.44,Default,,0,0,0,,稍等我一下
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.29,0:18:24.79,Default,,0,0,0,,你好 辛苦你了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.70,0:18:27.43,Default,,0,0,0,,好的 好的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.49,0:18:29.88,Default,,0,0,0,,原来是这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.20,0:18:32.87,Default,,0,0,0,,明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.24,0:18:43.61,Default,,0,0,0,,好的 好的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.44,0:18:46.04,Default,,0,0,0,,那麻烦你了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.51,0:18:48.66,Default,,0,0,0,,抱歉 橘…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.63,0:19:04.97,Default,,0,0,0,,时不时叫我忧心的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.92,0:19:08.00,Default,,0,0,0,,是她的年轻和纯洁
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.61,0:19:12.79,Default,,0,0,0,,以及对自己不再年轻的无地自容
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.97,0:19:19.68,Default,,0,0,0,,抱歉 我得回去店里一趟
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.96,0:19:22.82,Default,,0,0,0,,不仅仅是因为别人的眼光
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.65,0:19:26.49,Default,,0,0,0,,最重要的 是我自己不想受伤
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.17,0:19:30.63,Default,,0,0,0,,她一定很无聊吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.24,0:19:32.35,Default,,0,0,0,,这是一定的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.66,0:19:33.64,Default,,0,0,0,,和我这种大叔约会
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.61,0:19:36.53,Default,,0,0,0,,甜蜜又苦涩的青春结束后
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.03,0:19:39.84,Default,,0,0,0,,留下来的只有痛苦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.04,0:19:46.17,Default,,0,0,0,,那“花园”见吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.90,0:19:48.51,Default,,0,0,0,,今天谢谢你了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.88,0:19:50.26,Default,,0,0,0,,不会 呃…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.76,0:19:52.25,Default,,0,0,0,,再见
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.37,0:20:49.69,Default,,0,0,0,,我回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.24,0:20:56.24,Default,,0,0,0,,晶 你怎么又去看同部电影了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.83,0:20:58.81,Default,,0,0,0,,你不是说无聊吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.47,0:21:01.44,Default,,0,0,0,,哪本是今天的宣传册？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.56,0:21:03.18,Default,,0,0,0,,我不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.72,0:21:05.16,Default,,0,0,0,,你干嘛要放一起啦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.68,0:21:07.46,Default,,0,0,0,,旧的不是叫你丢掉的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.55,0:21:09.63,Default,,0,0,0,,不都一样吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.94,0:21:10.78,Default,,0,0,0,,不一样啦！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.77,0:21:24.07,Default,,0,0,0,,绝对…不一样
Comment: 0,0:21:26.50,0:22:52.72,Default,,0,0,0,,【ED】
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:05.00,Default,,0,0,0,,
